OL,3,CLast-minute bookings and less money to
OL,4,Cspend: Uncertainty for tourism in Wales
OL,6,FIt has been a "very mixed picture" for
OL,7,Ftourism businesses this year, with
OL,8,Fself-catering accommodation said to be
OL,9,Fthe hardest hit by declining visitors
OL,10,Fand rising costs, Wales' leading
OL,11,Ftourism alliance has told ITV Wales.
OL,13,FAlmost half of self-catering
OL,14,Faccommodation businesses reported
OL,15,Fhaving fewer customers so far this
OL,16,Fyear than last year.
