OL,3,CLast-minute bookings and less money to
OL,4,Cspend: Uncertainty for tourism in Wales
OL,6,FThat's according to the Welsh
OL,7,FGovernment's recent Tourism Barometer,
OL,8,Fwhich provides a regular snapshot of
OL,9,Findustry performance and gathered
OL,10,Fbusinesses' views in June this year.
OL,12,F60% of businesses reporting lower
OL,13,Fvisitor numbers say a lack of
OL,14,Fdisposable income or global economic
OL,15,Funcertainty have been contributing
OL,16,Ffactors.
OL,18,FThere is also a strong trend emerging
OL,19,Ftowards last-minute bookings.
