OL,3,CLast-minute bookings and less money to
OL,4,Cspend: Uncertainty for tourism in Wales
OL,6,FIt means only one in six operators
OL,7,Fsaid they feel 'very confident' to
OL,8,Foperate profitably this year.
OL,10,FThe Welsh Government says it is
OL,11,Fworking closely with the industry to
OL,12,Fhelp address the challenges they face.
OL,14,F"We're seeing a very mixed picture,"
OL,15,FBethan Davies of Wales Tourism
OL,16,FAlliance told ITV Wales.
OL,18,F"What we're seeing across Wales is a
OL,19,Fchange in the patterns of visitors.
