OL,3,CLast-minute bookings and less money to
OL,4,Cspend: Uncertainty for tourism in Wales
OL,6,F"There are a number of tourism
OL,7,Forganisations that are nervous about
OL,8,Ftheir performance this year. Numbers
OL,9,Fare down. People who are staying
OL,10,Fovernight are down, so we've got far
OL,11,Fmore day visitors than we used to have.
OL,13,F"And people are finding the cost of
OL,14,Fliving really impacting on their spend
OL,15,Fat the moment."
OL,17,FBethan Davies also hit out at the
OL,18,Ftourism tax proposed by the Welsh
OL,19,FGovernment, saying she finds it "very
OL,20,Fdifficult to believe it is going to
OL,21,Fwork in most of Wales."
