OL,3,CLast-minute bookings and less money to
OL,4,Cspend: Uncertainty for tourism in Wales
OL,6,F"I think adding #40 a week for a
OL,7,Ffamily of four staying in self-
OL,8,Fcatering accommodation is going to
OL,9,Fmake a massive difference.
OL,11,F"Would you come here to a beach in
OL,12,FTrearddur Bay, or would you go to a
OL,13,Fbeach in Morecambe and save #40 and
OL,14,Fhave an extra night out with the
OL,15,Ffamily?"
OL,17,FThe Visitor Levy Bill, which was
OL,18,Fapproved in the Senedd in July, would
OL,19,Fgive councils the power to charge up
OL,20,Fto #1.30 per person, per night,
OL,21,Fdepending on the type of accommodation.
