OL,6,FThe Welsh Government says the levy
OL,7,Fcould raise around #33 million a year
OL,8,Fto help fund infrastructure and local
OL,9,Fservices in tourist hotspots,
OL,10,Fincluding the upkeep of footpaths,
OL,11,Fpublic toilets and waste collections.
OL,13,F"These reports lay bare the economic
OL,14,Fdamage being inflicted on Welsh
OL,15,Ftourism," said Nicky Williamson,
OL,16,FProfessional Association of Self-
OL,17,FCaterers (PASC) UK's Lead Policy
OL,18,FAdvisor in Wales.
