OL,3,CLast-minute bookings and less money to
OL,4,Cspend: Uncertainty for tourism in Wales
OL,6,F"What we are witnessing is the
OL,7,Favoidable erosion of a vital sector,
OL,8,Fone that sustains jobs, communities,
OL,9,Fand Welsh culture. The figures are
OL,10,Fshocking, but not surprising to those
OL,11,Fof us on the ground."
OL,13,FMs Williamson said that the 182-day
OL,14,Frule, which requires properties to be
OL,15,Flet for at least 182 days to qualify
OL,16,Fas a holiday let, as especially
OL,17,Fdamaging.
