OL,6,FSuzy Farr, bookings manager for
OL,7,FTrearddur Bay Holiday Homes on
OL,8,FAnglesey, says she is optimistic for
OL,9,Fthe future, but the business has had
OL,10,Fto adapt to survive ` with people
OL,11,Fhaving less money and making more last-
OL,12,Fminute plans.
OL,14,F"We are busy right across the board.
OL,15,FThings have changed in the last
OL,16,Feighteen months," she told ITV Wales.
