OL,3,CLast-minute bookings and less money to
OL,4,Cspend: Uncertainty for tourism in Wales
OL,6,F"There's a lot of bookings last-
OL,7,Fminute, but we've adapted by changing
OL,8,Fthings to a 3-day travel away Friday
OL,9,Fto Monday, Monday to Friday getaways
OL,10,Fand long-term getaways. It has changed
OL,11,Fconsiderably in the last eighteen
OL,12,Fmonths though."
OL,14,F"Things have become a lot more
OL,15,Fexpensive, and so that people can come
OL,16,Faway, we've adapted."
