OL,6,FPhil Brown, owner of the Sea Shanty
OL,7,FCafe in Trearddur Bay, said that
OL,8,Fhospitality is facing difficult
OL,9,Fchallenges, so tourists visiting the
OL,10,Farea play a crucial role in staying
OL,11,Fafloat.
OL,13,F"We are doing our best to bring people
OL,14,Fhere, and I think we've succeeded. And
OL,15,Fother businesses have opened up since
OL,16,Fwe started," he said.
