OL,6,F"Trearddur Bay has become a
OL,7,Fdestination, and why not?"JHe added:
OL,8,F"People say there are less people here
OL,9,Fthis year than there were last year...
OL,10,FI don't know.
OL,12,F"But I think if you come here, you
OL,13,Fhaven't got to go to an airport,
OL,14,Fthere's so much going for Wales but
OL,15,Fthey don't seem good at marketing
OL,16,Fthemselves, which is a shame."
OL,18,FA Welsh Government spokesperson said,
OL,19,F"Tourism makes an important
OL,20,Fcontribution to the Welsh economy and
OL,21,Fto Welsh life.
