OL,6,F"Wales has so much to offer, and we
OL,7,Fwant to ensure that we realise that
OL,8,Fpotential in a way that achieves a
OL,9,Fbalance between our communities,
OL,10,Fbusinesses, landscapes and visitors.
OL,12,F"We work closely with the industry to
OL,13,Fhelp address the challenges they face.
OL,14,FSector-specific support is available
OL,15,Fto businesses through Visit Wales via
OL,16,Fcapital investment funding, marketing
OL,17,Fcampaigns to promote the whole of
OL,18,FWales, year-round and other support
OL,19,Ffor activities to boost the
OL,20,Fcontribution of tourism and
OL,21,Fhospitality to the Welsh economy."
